This packages installs OpenVanilla Loader 0.6.3 with pre-bundled input methods. OpenVanilla is an "input method" framework that is able to load various input method modules. This packages also comes with several Chinese input method modules that are popular among users of Traditional Chinese. Extras and additional input methods (such as modules or data files for Simplified Chinese) can be downloaded at our website 
\f1 http://openvanilla.org
